---i love you you love me ---

Halu bby! It's been a pretty stressful week for the both of us. Ikaw nastress kase late sahod mo sa PRI tas nakakahighblood talaga yung trato nila sa nurses nila. Tapos ako naman stressed and anxious sa state ng work ko ss GOIN huhu.

Pero wala lang, I just want to be thankful na despite all of our problems, we coudl still rely on each other. I just want to thank you bby kase I could always rely on you and depend on you for support on whatever problem, how big (yung work ko) and small (yung steam deck charger lol) man sila. 

And I also want to thank you for also depending on me with your problems. I'm happy that you find me as someone reliable and dependable enough for you to lean on, and I want it to continue that way because I love you sososos much my bby!! I'll be your number one support system! Always!!
